➜五大名窑中为什么定窑最为特殊？它美在哪个地方？
http://www.sohu.com/a/430427152_114960	41700
<p><span><strong>（央视财经《一槌定音》）</strong></span><span>今天的河北省曲阳</span><span>县涧</span><span>磁村一</span><span>带</span><span>，在唐代隶属于定州，定窑因此而得名。</span></p>
<p><span>作</span><span>为</span><span>宋代五大名窑之一的定窑，</span><span>拥</span><span>有着与其它四大名窑完全不同的独有特</span><span>质</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>汝窑、官窑、哥窑、</span><span>钧</span><span>窑、定窑，唯独定窑是以</span><span>烧</span><span>造白瓷</span><span>为</span><span>主。定瓷之白不是一</span><span>览</span><span>无</span><span>遗</span><span>的</span><span>纯</span><span>白，而是一种内</span><span>敛</span><span>、温</span><span>润</span><span>的白，白中微</span><span>闪</span><span>黄色，如玉之</span><span>润</span><span>。定瓷的瓷</span><span>质</span><span>精良、胎体</span><span>轻</span><span>薄，</span><span>这</span><span>便有了“白如玉、薄如</span><span>纸</span><span>、声如磬”之</span><span>说</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>除了</span><span>拥</span><span>有“天下第一白”的美誉，定瓷的</span><span>纹饰</span><span>更是如云</span><span>变</span><span>幻、</span><span>潇</span><span>洒奔逸。在宋代五大名窑中，定窑又是唯一以</span><span>纹样</span><span>装</span><span>饰见长</span><span>的窑口。定瓷的</span><span>纹样</span><span>装</span><span>饰</span><span>技法以印花、刻花和划花</span><span>为</span><span>主，印花技法，构成</span><span>严谨</span><span>、</span><span>图</span><span>案丰富多</span><span>样；</span><span>刻划花技法，灵</span><span>动潇</span><span>洒，如行云流水，</span><span>别</span><span>具一格。</span></p>
<p><span>北宋</span><span>时</span><span>期，定瓷生</span><span>产规</span><span>模庞大，</span><span>为</span><span>了适</span><span>应</span><span>大量生</span><span>产</span><span>的需要，定窑工匠</span><span>发</span><span>明了覆</span><span>烧</span><span>工</span><span>艺</span><span>。所</span><span>谓</span><span>覆</span><span>烧</span><span>，就是将碗或</span><span>盘</span><span>之</span><span>类</span><span>的器物倒</span><span>过</span><span>来，每件器物之</span><span>间</span><span>，在口沿部分用支圈</span><span>间</span><span>隔，</span><span>层层</span><span>相叠。覆</span><span>烧</span><span>的</span><span>优</span><span>点不</span><span>仅仅</span><span>是极大地增</span><span>强</span><span>了</span><span>产</span><span>能，它</span><span>还</span><span>充分利用了</span><span>热</span><span>效，</span><span>节约</span><span>了燃料，同</span><span>时烧</span><span>制的瓷器不易</span><span>变</span><span>形，提高了成品率。</span><span>这</span><span>一中国陶瓷史上的</span><span>伟</span><span>大</span><span>发</span><span>明，更是成就了定窑在宋代的地位。</span></p>
